    "---\n",
    "## Section 2: Event Normalizer\n",
    "\n",
    "Parse every CAPE JSON report into a flat list of typed events:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Category | Event types |\n",
    "|---|---|\n",
    "| Process | `process_create`, `process_inject` |\n",
    "| File | `file_write`, `file_delete`, `file_read` |\n",
    "| Registry | `reg_write`, `reg_delete`, `reg_read` |\n",
    "| Network | `dns_query`, `tcp_connect`, `http_request` |\n",
    "| Suspicious API | `suspicious_api_call` |"
   ]
  },
